    "exhibit recent advances in generative picture modelling by creating high-resolution, varied samples from big datasets like ImageNet that remains challenging.",
    "Orthogonal regularization reduces the generator's input variance, allowing a straightforward \"trade-off\" between sample integrity and variety.Your Local GAN [38] invented by Daras et al.",
    "utilizes two-dimensional geometry and locality are preserved based on sparse attention layer.",
    "They demonstrate that substituting SAGAN's thick attention layer in architecture improves FID, Inception score, and pure visuals significantly.",
    "ImageNet FID score improves from 18.65 to 15.94."
